Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.43,0:01:57.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高智能方程式的世界杯锦标赛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.75,0:02:00.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是转战于世界各地举行十场比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.22,0:02:05.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以每场赛事前六名所获得的积分总计
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.25,0:02:06.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来角逐世界冠军的梦幻车赛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.21,0:02:10.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了一般的赛车场以外
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.30,0:02:13.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有市街、山岳、沙漠以及雪原等
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.48,0:02:15.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各种用来考验赛车和选手极限的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.30,0:02:16.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超困难赛道来进行比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.72,0:02:20.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能够通过这些考验
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.28,0:02:22.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并得到最高积分的车手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.52,0:02:24.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将能得到被称为世界上最高速的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.49,0:02:26.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界冠军的荣耀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.65,0:02:30.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在英国杯首次拿到冠军
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.26,0:02:32.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隼人的积分向第一名大幅逼近
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.57,0:02:35.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此外兰德尔将从第六战开始参战
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.29,0:02:36.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界杯锦标赛的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.82,0:02:38.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于进入了后半段
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.14,0:02:45.14,Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(490.667,593.333)}{\blur1.333\bord0.333}冰上的死斗！第六战决胜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.98,0:02:54.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高智能方程式世界杯锦标赛第六战
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.14,0:02:56.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挪威杯的预赛时间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.34,0:02:58.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也即将接近尾声了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.15,0:03:00.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全长11.3公里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.84,0:03:04.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,利用挪威酷寒的大自然所创造出来的赛道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.26,0:03:06.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拥有被冰雪覆盖的最恶劣条件
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.67,0:03:09.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在世界杯锦标赛全十战的场地中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.38,0:03:11.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被公认是最苛酷的赛道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.67,0:03:14.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才新条直辉选手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.26,0:03:16.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始进行最后一次计时圈了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.74,0:03:21.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在纯白赛道上奔驰着的赤红赛车
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.33,0:03:23.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵车队的「火焰史培利昂」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.33,0:03:23.69,Tips,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(588.667,656.667)}Fire Superion G.T.R
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.62,0:03:27.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新条 状况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.75,0:03:30.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经掌握了火焰史培利昂的特性
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.87,0:03:31.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.31,0:03:41.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以推进器全力加速的最终弯道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.63,0:03:43.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要能掌握这里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.23,0:03:44.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就能拿下挪威杯的胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.22,0:03:46.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上吧「不死鸟之翼」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.22,0:03:46.96,Tips,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(549.333,656.667)}Phoenix Wing
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.22,0:04:07.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成绩揭晓了 是最快圈速
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.18,0:04:10.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新条直辉刷新了场地的最高纪录
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.16,0:04:15.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜你了 新条
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.79,0:04:16.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刷新场地记录了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.86,0:04:19.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没枉费去准备这辆新车了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.12,0:04:21.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,预赛还没有结束呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.88,0:04:25.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这句话还请你等到拿下杆位后再说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.64,0:04:26.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.48,0:04:28.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一名是新条吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.06,0:04:30.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听好了 隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.05,0:04:31.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别忘记车子是在冰上行走
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.28,0:04:33.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要慎重一点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.52,0:04:34.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.60,0:04:35.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.93,0:04:39.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第五战的胜利者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.11,0:04:41.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风见隼人的超级阿斯拉达进入赛道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.90,0:04:44.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在今天出道同为十四岁的兰德尔面前
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.78,0:04:46.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会有什么样的表现呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.40,0:04:48.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风见隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.46,0:05:01.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兰德尔 整备完毕了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.70,0:05:02.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随时可以出发
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.96,0:05:03.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.51,0:05:08.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微去做个了断
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.99,0:05:11.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路上请小心 少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.41,0:05:13.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好香的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.81,0:05:19.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请不要偏离了最短的测定路线
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.31,0:05:20.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.88,0:05:24.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即将通过中间点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.93,0:05:28.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通过中间点了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.80,0:05:30.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最佳记录
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.51,0:05:33.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,截至目前 比起新条直辉的纪录
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.42,0:05:34.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还要快上5秒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.44,0:05:36.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.24,0:05:37.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干得好 隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.69,0:05:40.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到最终弯道了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.62,0:05:41.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上吧 阿斯拉达
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.85,0:05:42.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,推进器启动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.82,0:05:48.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多么恐怖的G力…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.83,0:05:49.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体快要被挤扁了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.02,0:05:52.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.73,0:05:54.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.52,0:05:55.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.90,0:05:56.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.28,0:05:58.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,踩煞车太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.56,0:05:59.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用方向盘导正出弯角度
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.72,0:06:06.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.72,0:06:07.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时间呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.20,0:06:11.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呿 第二名吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.72,0:06:12.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经很好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.92,0:06:15.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是太勉强发生了事故 就一切都完了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.01,0:06:16.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说的没错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.27,0:06:18.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风见隼人选手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.61,0:06:20.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在最终弯道失误 损失了一点时间
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.84,0:06:22.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但还是漂亮的抵达终点了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.20,0:06:38.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要向你展示自己的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.42,0:06:39.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,证明自己比隼人更优秀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.54,0:06:43.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.66,0:06:46.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙竟然敢向我们下挑战书
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.98,0:06:51.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,预赛的时间只剩不到5分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.80,0:06:53.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万众瞩目的天才少年兰德尔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.81,0:06:55.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在进入赛道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.55,0:07:00.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没在那个倾斜弯道失误就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.55,0:07:00.32,Tips,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(483.333,656.667)}Bank
